<F P=100> ANNEX </F>
<F P=101> Yugoslavia, Kosovo </F>
<H3> <TI>   Institute Building Remains `Confiscated' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Institute Building Remains `Confiscated' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1506165094 Tirana ATA in English 0816 GMT 15 Jun 94 -- FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> AU1506165094 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana ATA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pristina, June 15 (ATA) -- The building of the 
Albanological Institute of Prishtina is being confiscated even 
after 10th of June, the deadline set by the Serbian installed 
prefect of Kosova, in which the premises of the institute should 
be returned to the Albanians. The employees' institute say that 
the building might be given back to them. 

</TEXT>

