<F P=106> [Report by Mirza Sadikovic from Bihac] </F>
  [Text] In the afternoon, the united aggressor intensified 
the attacks on the free territory of the Bihac district. The 
outskirts of the Cazin commune have become the target of the 
artillery from the strongholds in the so-called Serbian 
Autonomous Region of Krajina. The members of the treacherous 
Abdic's phalanxes have started new artillery and infantry 
attacks on (?Trsac), Krivaja, (?Vidkovac), [word indistinct], 
and (?Kodrovi). They have been bringing fresh forces and 
military hardware all the time, especially to the area around 
Vidkovac and Pecigrad. Karadzic's chetniks on the Bihac, 
Bosanska Krupa, and Buzim part of the front have been attacking 
with antiaircraft arms. Their infantry arms provocations lasted 
the entire day, while their sniper fire has intensified, too. 
The reliable reports claim that there are indications that 
Abdic's war-mongering headquarters in Velika Kladusa has been 
arresting the workers of [words indistinct] and marching them 
through the town as captured members of the 5th Corps. 

