  [Text] Bucharest ROMPRES, 16/6/1994 -- During a news 
conference on June 16, in Oradea, reformed Bishop Laszlo Tokes, 
mentioned that the article speaking about him and issued 
recently in the TINERAMA newspaper "seemed unrealistic, a 
diversion built by the Securitate, in close connection with the 
present power and the nationalist extremists." 
  In the article in TINERAMA, journalist Ioan Itu supposed the 
