standpoint according to which Romania has to become member of 
the "Central-European initiative." "These aspects, associated 
with the visit President Vaclav Havel will pay the next few days 
to Bucharest, prove a real will at this moment for an 
intensification of the bilateral relations", Adrian Nastase 
stated. 

