<H3> <TI>   SDSS Breakaway Faction Seen as HZDS `Game' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    SDSS Breakaway Faction Seen as HZDS `Game' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1706192294 Bratislava SLOVENSKY DENNIK in Slovak 15 Jun 94 
p 2 </F>

<F P=103> AU1706192294 </F>
<F P=104>  Bratislava SLOVENSKY DENNIK </F>
<F P=105>  Slovak </F>


<TEXT>
