  [Text] The Social Democratic Party of Hungary [MSZDP] wants 
to form a cooperation agreement before the local government 
elections with the Hungarian Socialist Party and the trade 
unions. The MSZDP's executive authorized the party's Presidium 
to begin discussions with other left-wing forces which accept 
the importance of social-democratic ideas in Hungary's political 
and economic life, the MSZDP's statement says. 

